<emphasis id="C5FB0F386E0C1B52E7136B07FF2857B6" bold="true" box="[101,252,888,909]" pageId="8">Bibliography.</emphasis>
Louis, Engberg et al. (2006), Mittermeier et al. (2010).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
